name: Conte Sans_85% (iOS14)
author: Evelyn (ev_ynw)
description:
85% size. Install 'Conte Sans' for normal character size.

Only compatible on iOS14. Separate packages for iOS10-12 and iOS13 are available.

Installed to: /Library/Themes/[fontname].theme/

Apply with Anemone. Package name = Fonts.

Need help? Link to tutorials in my pinned tweet
